## Description {#details}

Represents a YAML sequence created from either a block sequence for a flow sequence.

This parses the YAML stream as <a href="#a5848780917af6e4008594d684aaaa9db">increment()</a> is called.

Example:
<ul>
<li>Hello</li>
<li>World</li>
</ul>
